Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜 我出去下就回来 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.79,0:00:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 送别的时候应该说什么话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 我会陪真琴玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.19,0:00:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么忙还麻烦你真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己想陪真琴一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对么 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妈妈一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙已经连话都不会说了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本不会笑也不生气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在逐渐失去人类一般的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在秋子阿姨和名雪都在帮我照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她不知怎么对于我之外的人都放不下戒心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能和她见个面么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这对你来说很残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想你的话应该可以理解这一切 让她接受你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:03:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}第10话\N山丘上的镇魂歌\N～requiem～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我叫做天野见汐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字 有名字的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做她就能安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试着想想看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…呜…真…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真？“真”的后面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…琴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…琴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这个人又叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一直叫他的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…呜…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…祐…一…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐…一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 你想起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起 真努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是一时的恢复 马上又会忘记的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当她再次发烧昏睡的时候 估计就是…那个时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这孩子有想要完成的心愿的话 无论如何请满足她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要完成的心愿…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那时买给她更好的礼物该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想要做的事情么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还有很多想要做的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管想做什么我都陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔这样也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 好久没有出去吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的就多吃点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对么 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 大家一起拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大头贴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里拍的照片可以做成贴纸的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错 一起去拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 去拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真窄呢 不知道挤不挤的下四个人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要推我 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像蛮难操作的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学生都会用 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可以不用光看 你也来一起拍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 跟我们一起拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 快来吧 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 来吧 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 真琴在当中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 好像可以书写输入文字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么 那就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那个来写吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴也准备好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三 二 笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上 真琴又发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 醒了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧 稍微舒服点了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想要的东西么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不我去买肉包子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:08:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴只要和我在一起就好了对么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这样就满足了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 读书给你听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你最喜欢的书哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要睡着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就读给你听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始了 开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱总是那么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这孩子有想要完成的心愿的话 无论如何请满足她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 一定会来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到那时 两人就再也不分开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我结婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要…结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和祐一结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我结婚吧 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 真琴能起床了么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 接下来准备两个人出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又逃学吗 真是不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会做好美味的晚饭等你们回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃课了么 看来我们两个都不是什么好学生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了这些 我其它都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我们是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来准备先去学校 然后去那座山丘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么 是个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座山丘是这孩子出生的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我就送到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 麻烦你传达下消息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 水濑名雪同学是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 什么时候再一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只是想和你玩一会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 不过现在是午休所以没有太多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:11:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想玩什么呢 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 回来之后再一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多话想要对真琴说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 那么待会见 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴也坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 是肉包子 喜欢吃多少就吃多少哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 差不多该开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 真琴 还醒着么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有钱买整套的婚纱 所以只有这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用手压好 不要让风吹跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 相泽祐一与泽渡真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论对方生病或健康、富裕或贫穷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都发誓一生永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后我们永远在一起 好么 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这样真琴的愿望就得以实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像孩子一样胡闹给大家捣蛋的真琴应该是幸福的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟讨厌的我在一起的真琴应该是幸福的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切难道都是为了报恩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实大家都很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一直都在吵架 我也是最喜欢你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.09,0:15:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你能察觉到这一切的话 那你应该是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你老是喜欢和人闹别扭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这点让我有些担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 我们要永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 不要哭了 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面纱什么的根本无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可是个值得庆祝的日子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始我们是真正的家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 好了 不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 靠过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你揉揉头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 玩这个吧 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会发出叮铃叮铃的声音哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴也试着摇摇看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢这样子玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴么 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 真琴 轮到你了 快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要睡啊 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 玩铃铛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好玩的哦 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对 接下来轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直能这样玩那该多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 轮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得见么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.83,0:17:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拨弄它会叮铃叮铃响的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啊 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 在那里做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 跟我们一起拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点过来 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 真琴在当中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴也准备好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三 二 笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天来了 如果一直都是春天多好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你这么精神我也放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只有这个优点了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到了春天…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到了春天 又能看到它们在山丘上奔跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在渺小的生活中 又会孕育出新的生命并被抚养长大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后其中又会出现向往人类的温暖的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也说不定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那也没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是那些孩子的天性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定 这个城镇里半数以上的人都是那些孩子所化的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是没有人察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定大家都不是人类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如我 或是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 不要吓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 若是住在那山丘上的狐狸都拥有不可思议的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那些孩子很多聚集在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定可以创造不得了的奇迹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在说梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上掉点心的话 不觉得是件很棒的事么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉在地上的点心可是很脏的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相泽同学太现实了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 没想到还喜欢这种少女趣味的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们 做了个同样的梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后梦醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 有奇迹发生的话 相泽同学会希望什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还需要说么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.11,0:23:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又是那个人干的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.94,0:23:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不理解你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.20,0:23:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是个有名的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.96,0:24:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我觉得我肯定可以跟亚由成为好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.73,0:24:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为就算说了也没人会相信
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26\fad(300,0)}第11话\N光与影的间奏曲\N～intermezzo～
